{"tid":771584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google食回頭草？ 人民日報：中國歡迎你","createTime":"2018-08-08T05:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T11:42:54.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c146b4035dd380014b42f2e5d3bf640333bde1","tid":771584,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180808/large/b0101a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180808%2Flarge%2Fb0101a.gif&h=5761e80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國網企三巨頭BAT，即百度、阿里、騰訊（700），過往一直獲網絡防火牆庇護，今年或迎來最大挑戰。內地官方就Google入華再度釋出善意，《人民日報》昨於海外社交媒體Twitter及facebook刊登文章，表示歡迎Google回歸中國市場，但前提是要遵守中國法律。BAT股價今年已大幅跑輸美國科網股，內地再對美國科技公司打開大門，BAT股價料繼續受壓。<br />\n記者：黃尹華<br />\n<br />\n如Google入華，<span style=\"color: red;\">百度將最受衝擊，其董事長李彥宏昨發文稱，「如果現在Google回來，我們正好可以真刀真槍地再PK（對決）一次，再贏一次。」</span>內地網民普遍抨擊李彥宏言論，有網民指其言論無恥，之前沒有贏過，何來「再贏。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180808/large/08bm02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180808%2Flarge%2F08bm02p.jpg&h=c7dbe4f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">■Google若成功重返中國，有力挑戰內地科網巨頭；左起為騰訊馬化騰、阿里馬雲及百度李彥宏。資料圖片<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180808/large/b0101b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180808%2Flarge%2Fb0101b.gif&h=d9eeefe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「歡迎回歸　須遵守中國法律」</strong><br />\n<br />\nGoogle母企Alphabet股價造好，截至本港昨晚約9時40分，報1241.9美元，升1.39%；相反百度報255.23美元，跌3.32%。雖然最終入華的可能是「跪低版」Google，但內地網民表現雀躍，甘之如飴。自2010年Google撤出中國後，內地網民只能使用百度做網上搜索，除大量境外網站和敏感詞被遮罩外，百度採用商業競價排名的方式顯示搜索結果，嚴重影響口碑。2016年，患重病的內地青年魏則西受百度誤導，接受違規療法致死，更在內地引起公憤。<br />\n<br />\n在去年11月，中國國家互聯網資訊辦公室國際合作局長祁小夏已表示，若Google、facebook及Twitter等美國互聯網企業，願意接受及遵守內地監管審查及法律，「如果他們想要回來，我們歡迎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180808/large/b0101c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180808%2Flarge%2Fb0101c.gif&h=1544ef77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180808/large/b0101d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180808%2Flarge%2Fb0101d.gif&h=1f81e66e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>研發新軟件過濾敏感字眼</strong><br />\n<br />\nGoogle率先跪低換取人民幣。《人民日報》昨日在fb文章引述美國網上媒體《The Intercept》報道，Google正研發新的搜索軟件，估計可自動過濾敏感字眼，包括有關民主、人權及和平抗議等關鍵字或違反中國政府觀點的搜索字眼，對此表示歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n上月《The Intercept》已曾踢爆，極想入華的Google在去年秘密啟動一項名為Dragonfly（蜻蜓）的計劃，若發現網站屬未符合中國規定，將通通列入黑名單。報道當日，美國上市的百度股價急跌8%，市值跌破800億美元。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府對境外網絡管控，自2011的「阿拉伯民主之春」運動後更加嚴厲，除Google外，fb、Gmail、YouTube、Instagram均逐步遭到封殺。其間內地科網股逐步崛起，獨霸網絡社交媒體的騰訊更成為股王。<br />\n<br />\n今年起，市場已不斷傳出內地網絡可能鬆閘消息，如Google率先入閘，fb和其他科網巨頭願意配合「中國法律」，增加入華機會，百度、阿里、騰訊將受到衝擊。騰訊在港股通昨日再走資5億元，自7月以來已累計走資93億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180808/20471565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F20471565&d=xTomnt8%2Fnx7TIgb7e0FxbAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=70d085fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F20471565&h=7deaf057\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180808/20471565</a>"},{"pid":"2cbb619502afbac8f33632cd8bf4383d3822c491","tid":771584,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T05:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Google正研發新的搜索軟件，估計可自動過濾敏感字眼，包括有關民主、人權及和平抗議等關鍵字或違反中國政府觀點的搜索字眼，對此表示歡迎。</blockquote><br />\n一個國家墮落到要禁止自己既人民為自己爭取民主、人權及和平抗議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 荒天下之大謬"},{"pid":"c36dc6424583699ed1b56d0b224d56a6f5a92f68","tid":771584,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:28:24.000Z","msg":"Google無撤出中國香港喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77da0ae9cb5cddaf3f379c418f1a8085f36aa244","tid":771584,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:30:32.000Z","msg":"我又唔信搜尋引擎會囉<br />\n其他就難講<br />\n<br />\n係中共下<br />\n咩公司搜尋引擎都一樣架啦<br />\n做黎做乜"},{"pid":"ada7e055210f119bb7ca6dbbecea65b5acf540b4","tid":771584,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:40:02.000Z","msg":"google  為成 大陸版 百度, 被監控. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都好過用百度."},{"pid":"7edee376d1295abe6adaf9f5461bfb10894a2938","tid":771584,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:44:11.000Z","msg":"有分析認為，若Google成大水魚，中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"28ac8401709bbaf3305c81a5a657e386a8a8e9fd","tid":771584,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:54:44.000Z","msg":"做人質??<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f16cbc4b043a7245b97978d62bda1a45ea448f","tid":771584,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"同FB一樣，無得睇外國嘢，<br />\n啲人點解要用你先？"},{"pid":"f112fab8b506ec3664920267a875ba337aaa28ef","tid":771584,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:31:10.000Z","msg":"點解咁多公司鐘意奶共？ 一陣俾人食埋就搞笑"},{"pid":"eed26e78f0d4115a9aa71d57a7f1bdba42a415d8","tid":771584,"uid":76715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Google咁無骨氣"}]}